# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

There are no existing structures to report as this is the first report.

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors related to fuel for drills
- The agent attempts to add coal to drills when there is no coal in the inventory. Ensure that there is coal in the inventory before attempting to add it to the drill.
- The agent attempts to extract iron ore from a drill that is out of fuel. Refuel the drill before attempting to extract iron ore.

### Errors related to transport belts
- The agent attempts to connect a transport belt to an inserter that is already connected. Check if the transport belt is already connected before attempting to connect it.
### Errors related to extracting from furnace
- The agent attempts to extract iron plates from a furnace when there are no iron plates in the furnace. Ensure that there are iron plates in the furnace before attempting to extract them.
### Errors when using extracting but not finding item
- The agent attempts to extract iron-ore from transport-belt but could not find a valid transport-belt entity containing iron-ore. Ensure that the transport belt contains the item before attempting to extract it.
